reviews.text: Love the McCafe at Fortress Hill with good barista. I have stopped going to the Starbucks opposite. I love it that this McDonald's does not drive the homeless away late at night when there is much less customers.
Located in tourists areas. Always queues line.  But services is quite fast. No need to wait too long.  With machine taken order it shortens time for those familiar with.

I live near a McDonald's but I always walk extra to come here for breakfast. I always get sausage egg McMuffin set with normal coffee, and every time the McMuffin is put together well, the hash brown is the best part, it is always cooked to perfection, every, single, time. 

The staff in the morning is super efficient too. However, I have come here in the evening and the staff is the completely opposite.

McDonald's is my favorite fast food joint worldwide, and it is also my Mom's favorite.

McDonald's knows how to cater to the market it is in.  They make items that the locals knows and loves.  Currently there is a special sandwich being served in Hong Kong , and it is called My Taste of Hong Kong. Now, just how special is that for Hong Kongese?  To have a McDonald's Signature collection sandwich named after your city.

A few years ago, maybe 10 plus.  That would still be a few years to me.  There was a Taro Pie which was fabulous to me and my family.  Anyone who loves Taro anything would have fallen in love with the Taro Pie which was only available in Hong Kong.

Then there was the Red Bean Pie that followed, which was also equally fabulous.  Both of the special pies was so so good to the pallet, I could never just eat 1.  Not too sweet and the Taro was fresh (I think).   I missed the McDonald's Taro Pie so much that I look for it everytime I visited Hong Kong, but to no avail so far.  

FYI, Mickey D's  Fries are  my favorite fast food fries.
Nice  and tidy  place, very calm and relax when your  are having your meal.

reviews.text: 玉子牛肉好吃😋
好多閒雜人，尤其多垃圾保險sales，經常霸住晒靚位同客傾，連買包薯條都唔捨得，so cheap!
場地位置唔錯 食物質素 都係差唔多啦 服務員工 態度 都ok嘅 只係 高檔啲嘅咖啡那邊 員工比較機械 禮貌死板 星期六日 賓妹多個菲律賓 連樓梯你都行唔到 冷氣 當然 唔係好夠
好耐未食過蘋果批咁新鮮熱辣👍👍 喺砲台山呢一間麥當勞終於食到啦，因為人流多，所以食物新鮮， 包類薯條都熱辣辣 ， 呢度沖啲咖啡都好正 ，而且呢間的經理好友善，速度好快👏👏
